Better Homes & Gardens Real Estate Bloomtree Realty

data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 10-acres parcel of land, this meticulously crafted manufactured home, completed in 2021, offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities and natural surroundings. Enclosed by a secure no climb fencing, the property ensures privacy while showcasing stunning views. The home itself boasts a welcoming open floor plan, featuring exposed beams in the expansive great room and kitchen area. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, complemented by laminate flooring that flows throughout the interior. In the great room, a built-in cabinet with wiring for a flat-screen TV adds a touch of convenience and style. With four bedrooms, two full baths, and an additional family room, the residence provides ample space for comfortable living. The bathrooms feature executive height counters and dual sink vanities, while the bedrooms offer plush carpeting for added comfort. A dedicated laundry room adds practicality to the layout. The property is environmentally conscious with its owned solar system, contributing to energy efficiency. RV hook-ups installed. Conveniently located near the highway, residents enjoy easy access to shopping, schools, entertainment, and medical facilities, making this home a perfect blend of modern living and scenic tranquility.
